                We live in an amazing country that offers us so many opportunities, diversities and national parks to visit for free this year! To honour Canada’s 150th birthday, we’d love to know the reason you love Canada – submit your reason in the form below to spread the awareness of #150Reasons.
 <br><br>
#150Reasons is an initiative brought to you by VIBE Arts, an innovative and award-winning charitable organization that provides young people across the country with the opportunity to share their voice through art.
 <br><br>
For the month of June, Scarborough Town Centre will be exhibiting hand-painted murals that express the unique spirit of Canada, created by youth from every Province and Territory. Visit the centre to take in the meaningful stories expressed in each mural that tells the story of our country through the eyes of Canada’s youth and honours the diversity, culture, character and strength of our great nation.
 
